text:
Chuck Carlton, Big 12 football beat writer for SportsDayDFW.com and The Dallas Morning News, answers your questions about the league in a live chat at 11 a.m. Tuesday. Ask your questions in the ScribbleLive module below, and Chuck will discuss them for an hour or so.
